-移动的2种方法
1.public float speed=0.3f
transform.translate(Vector3.forward*Time.deltatime*speed)
2.public float speed =0.3f;
float translation=Input.GetAxis("Verticle")*speed*Time.deltatime;
transform.translate(0,0,translation);//这个是沿Z移动



